{"tid":879150,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次養貓，佢唔肯飲水","createTime":"2018-10-27T16:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T01:12:49.000Z","uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b9797dc966bb53eb0cd287b0bf3ee171ccc3d1","tid":879150,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"3個月大，<br />\n每日分三餐食一罐5.5oz Wellness<br />\n每次都有另外加少少水溝開<br />\n但我估應該唔夠每日所需<br />\n<br />\n個籠入面會放一碗水<br />\n日日都換水，但佢從來都唔會飲<br />\n<br />\n同埋喺廳都開咗個小佩飲水機<br />\n但係佢有幾次行埋去聞兩嘢就跑走<br />\n應該係驚個水機<br />\n<br />\n好擔心佢飲唔夠水，<br />\n因為養佢呢兩個星期真係未見過佢飲水<br />\n有無方法可以訓練佢唔驚部飲水機？"},{"pid":"89704c213627c90dd106945927d66f0674d5c248","tid":879150,"uid":60514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"試下係水度加啲貓草"},{"pid":"3ecda6401e1722618fc4202579ff76c13fe9c688","tid":879150,"uid":139439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"b2d0fb258c556d43075c78df7051768eecd8d821","tid":879150,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89704c213627c90dd106945927d66f0674d5c248","tid":879150,"uid":60514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"試下係水度加啲貓草"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T23:13:48.000Z","msg":"貓抓板加咗貓草都無興趣<br />\n暫時對貓草係無咩反應<br />\n<br />\n同埋部機都會過濾走d草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be85748be2d08624f1f88c11094ca91126e65b1","tid":879150,"uid":36164,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T23:26:09.000Z","msg":"咦原來罐糧叫Nature&rsquo;s Variety Instinct<br />\n唔敢同佢轉乾糧，驚佢唔識要飲水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDbZtKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDbZtKy.jpg&h=0dc46c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HnBvXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HnBvXU.jpg&h=98d4822c&s={SIZE}\" /